Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:17.51,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}一定會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:31.64,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}你眼中所見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:35.00,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}是否都是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:38.68,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}在糾葛化解之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:43.83,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}你有何感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:47.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}睜開眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:53.63,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}再是貪婪也能相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:59.66,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}悲傷中依憑那份理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:03.35,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}這樣又有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:09.65,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}毫無修飾而得到的美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:13.99,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}你總有天要明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.89,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}不管身在何方
